Package aprove.Framework.IntTRS.Nonterm.GeoNonTerm.ReversePolishNotationTree

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RPNConstant
    The RPNConstant represents a TRSConstantTerm within the RPNTree (reverse polish notation tree).
    RPNFunctionSymbol
    The RPNFunctionSymbol represents a TRSCompoundTerm within the RPNTree (reverse polish notation tree).
    RPNNode
    The RPNNode is an abstract node in the binary RPNTree (reverse polish notation tree).
    RPNTreeParser
    The RPNTreeParser provides a static method to parse a TRSTerm into a RPNTree using RPNNode.
    RPNVariable
    A RPNVariable represents a TRSVariable within the RPNTree (reverse polish notation tree).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ArithmeticSymbol
    The enum type of the supported arithmetical operators within the RPNTree used mainly within the RPNFunctionSymbol.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportetArithmeticSymbolException
    The UnsupportetArithmeticSymbolException is a subclass of Exception and is used to indicate that an other ArithmeticSymbol than + (PLUS), - (MINUS) or * (TIMES) is used.
